  <Section Title="Declaration">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[class NullLogger : public ILogger;]]></Code>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>NullLogger</TypeRef> class is an <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.ILogger">ILogger</PageRef> implementation that discards every log message.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      A null logger reports an empty scope, reports every severity as disabled, and creates new null loggers when cloned or when a child scope is requested. This makes it useful as a default object where code expects a logger but no output should be produced.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
